Luis is senior data engineer at Mind Candy, was the first to introduce Spark Streaming at the company, and is responsible for the real-time mobile analytics platform. He has more than 10 years of experience in software engineering and architecture.

@emre

Emre is Qubit’s co-founder and CTO. Qubit is a provider of an integrated web personalization, a/b testing, audience segmentation, and digital analytics platform. Prior to starting Qubit, he was a senior product manager at Google working on AdWords and AdSense products – building large scale artificial intelligence and analytics systems to scale and automate operations. Prior to Google, Emre was the co-founder and CTO of Yonja.com, Turkey’s largest social network.
When not thinking big data and personalization, Emre finds himself either kitesurfing or Olympic trap shooting.

